M: Right. Every year, nearly two million people
visit this park to enjoy the scenery and fun
activities.
W: What activities can visitors do there?
M: Well, they can enjoy horseback riding, bungee
jumping, and many other exciting activities.
W: Sounds enjoyable. Is camping allowed there?
M: Yes. There’s a campsite inside the park.
W: Good. Thanks, Larry.
